# Claude Code session state (scheduled_tasks.lock, plans, tool outputs).
# Ignore contents by default, but share the SessionStart hook and its wiring
# so every Claude Code on the web session pre-warms the Gradle cache
# (sandbox tool-execution cannot reach dl.google.com — SessionStart can).
.claude/*
!.claude/hooks/
.claude/hooks/*
!.claude/hooks/session-start.sh
!.claude/hooks/block-heredoc-commit.sh
!.claude/settings.json
